      "comment": "WISECRACKER (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 297m behind Bruiser My Uncle (17.91) in a Grade 4/5. Can discover winning form. GIVE ME ROOM (2) had been going along well winning a Grade 6 three back then placing at this track before missing the frame latest when fourth (17.78) at this track. Expected to do much better this time. CHAROS DREAM (4) scored a most impressive win two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 4 length 4th at this track (17.73). Expected to give a good account. GLOW GIRL (7) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
